# Settings UI hints

Read docs/SETTINGS_UI.md before editing Plugin Manager settings.

- Every setting needs hint text (range, default, behavior).
- Numeric settings use slider + edit_field in one row via Core/SettingsUI.lua.
- Do not strip hints to fit the 200-line gate — extend SettingsUI.lua instead.
